OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774023077
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after 'attempting
OL,4,Cto enter nuclear naval base' in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FA 34-year-old man, understood to be
OL,8,FIranian, has been arrested after
OL,9,Ftrying to get into the naval base in
OL,10,FScotland where Britain's nuclear
OL,11,Fsubmarines are based.
OL,13,FPolice Scotland said that the man, and
OL,14,Fa 31-year-old woman, were arrested on
OL,15,FThursday following the incident at HM
OL,16,FNaval Base Clyde, which is known as
OL,17,FFaslane.
OL,19,FThe site is home to the core of the
OL,20,FUK's submarine fleet and the Trident
OL,21,Fnuclear deterrent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
