PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774023077
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after 'attempting
OL,4,Cto enter nuclear naval base' in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FIt is understood that the pair did not
OL,8,Ftry to force their way into the base.
OL,9,FRather, they asked if they could enter
OL,10,Fbut were refused permission and were
OL,11,Fthen arrested shortly afterwards,
OL,12,Faccording to authorities.
OL,14,FA Navy spokesperson said: "Police
OL,15,FScotland have arrested two people who
OL,16,Funsuccessfully attempted to enter HM
OL,17,FNaval Base Clyde on Thursday 19 March.
OL,19,F"As the matter is subject to an
OL,20,Fongoing investigation, we will not
OL,21,Fcomment further."
