OL,3,CTwo people arrested after 'attempting
OL,4,Cto enter nuclear naval base' in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FA Police Scotland spokesman said:
OL,8,F"Around 5pm on Thursday, 19 March,
OL,9,F2026, we were made aware of two people
OL,10,Fattempting to enter HM Naval Base
OL,11,FClyde.
OL,13,F"A 34-year-old man and 31-year-old
OL,14,Fwoman have been arrested in connection
OL,15,Fand enquiries are ongoing."
